 not become well-known until several decades after Etymologi was written.

33
00:03:01.480 --> 00:03:08.400
 The ninth book discusses languages, peoples, kingdoms, armies, cities, and titles.

34
00:03:08.400 --> 00:03:13.540
 It outlines in detail the nations that sprang from the three sons of Noah after the

35
